---
title: Mild Pork Thai Red Curry with Veggie Stir-Fry & Garlic Rice
description: Elevate your pork dining experience with this veggie-packed stir-fry! Sticky and fragrant, this dish is ready in the blink of an eye and will satisfy all your stir-fry needs. Fluffy jasmine rice is a must to soak up all that rich sticky sauce.
